Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detect a few things that seem out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:03.87,teevee,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\pos(1166,178)\fs8\c&HCE546C&\3c&HFFEBF0&\fscx300\fscy300\blur0.5}High School Student and Detective Prince
