Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I cannot divulge details at this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I will say that something feels off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, um... Shirogane?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:16.88,teevee,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\pos(1166,178)\fs8\c&HCE546C&\3c&HFFEBF0&\fscx300\fscy300\blur0.5}High School Student and Detective Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:16.88,teevee,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\pos(1169,206)\fs8\c&HCE546C&\3c&HFFEBF0&\fscx300\fscy300\blur0.5}Searching for the Truth About the Murders
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met him at the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this matter claimed the lives of three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, I believe even the smallest inconsistency must be investigated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was kinda surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The distinguished Detective Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you talking about the report last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think he was the type to go after the spotlight like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer not to go on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:53.12,signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(713,27)\pos(716,177)\fnBE Blob\fs35\bord0\fsp3\b1\frx2\fax-0.07\fry0\frz6.178\c&H1950B4&\blur0.6}JUST LIKE MAMA'S COOKING
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:53.12,signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(704,90)\pos(705,214)\fnBE Blob\fs45\bord0\fsp3\c&H0C7366&\frx4\fax-0.07\fry358\blur0.6\frz6.858}SOU{\c&H1950B4&}ZAI DAI{\c&H0C7366&}GAKU
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could you please indulge my current theory on the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The case is already closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say something felt wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, regarding commonalities between the victims...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them were kidnapped before they were murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victims were all locals who had been the focus of recent media attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,becoming suddenly well-known.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe there's anything intrinsically unique about the victims themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you admit that a number of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fit these identical circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you figure that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a long interval between the second and third deaths in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I discovered several similar disappearances had taken place that fit the aforementioned criteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagi Yukiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi Kanji,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kujikawa Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you disappeared shortly after being shown on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either you escaped death somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or you faked your own disappearances to divert attention from yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since some of you had ties to the victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps one of you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, hold it! What—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! Isn't that the Detective Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take this elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you think that one of us is the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I considered that possibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now I believe exactly the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't the culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be the only ones with the means to pursue the true perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seen as a joining of forces between the rescued,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:06:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything falls into place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a flaw in the theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't account for Mr. Morooka's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has never been broadcast on television nor gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must also consider the condition of his corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was hung upside-down just like Ms. Yamano and Konishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true he was found in a similar position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first two victims are still listed with an unknown cause of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Mr. Morooka died of an easily identifiable blunt force trauma to the occipital cranium.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police have not satisfactorily resolved this discrepancy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet they are desperate to close the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Further action will be necessary to obtain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,decisive evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will this pan out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said something interesting to me not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We go into the TV to rescue people after they get kidnapped."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a game for me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that Naoto on the Midnight Channel last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It definitely looked like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Teddie, and he said no one's on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't we already catch the killer?{dumb bitch}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the case is closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why did he show up on the Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is the Midnight Channel, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Detective Prince, Shirogane Naoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to "Experiment of the Century: The Genome Project."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be both {>}experimenter and experimentee in a bodily alteration process!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will use a forbidden yet wonderful process!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall witness my departure into a new realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment of a new birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the chosen day forth, I shall walk a completely different path in life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will share this glorious occasion with all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do stay tuned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,625)}Hel—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just saw N-Naoto crystal clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,625)}Calm—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we caught the damn killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This proves that Naoto's gut feeling was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good was it when he got himself kidnapped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, he pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to gather the group?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Sniff, sniff!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely someone in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this world is growing larger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My nose is worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to rub your shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't distract her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean the case isn't over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's still happening like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Naoto suddenly decided to go on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only locals who've been on TV have been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made himself bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He could get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The least he coulda done was warn us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said this wasn't a game to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of what I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rise...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use{DAME}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell he's here, but I can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous to wander around blindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd lose our bear-ings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if the case isn't over,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what's the deal with Kubo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he kill King Moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what Naoto said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird how they could only identify Mr. Morooka's cause of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's the only one who never entered the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:11:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer didn't change his methods with King Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a different killer to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the person who kidnapped Naoto is the real culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kubo confessed that he killed the others, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he took the rap for someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's something else bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about someone behind bars?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, that idiot's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I need more information so I can get a better picture of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More info, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know shit about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and gather information on Naoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if this is related to Naoto or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but hasn't the town seemed weird as of late?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone seems strangely happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're always talking about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing new, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it their way of showing they're relieved that the case is closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they're afraid of something.{FORESHADOWING}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{eyecatch}
