Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}The Detective Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Oh, doesn't he have like seven secretaries?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}It's so cool how he gets a different one every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Care to pick me up and make me your secretary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}every day of the week?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Shuddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}He was awful!{not sure if this should be an8?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Talk about gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Satonaka hasn't had any luck yet either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}This town's friggin' puny,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}so why can't we find any useful info?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}He stands out like a sore thumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy right—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My old lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,got taken to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought someone here, not the other way around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shout in a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the poor boy get hit by a bicycle right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he hit his head, I wanted him to see a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they said he's fine. Isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're shouting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go down without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:14:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those stuffed animals you made to boost store profits are quite popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're knitted animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not stuffed animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, everyone's driving me nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.42,signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnEmbryonic Outside\fs85\bord4\c&H8CD3F2&\blur1\3c&H077AF5&\frz17.27\pos(417,447)}Aiya
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it wasn't anything serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make up for lost time after we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulling shit like that, never considering how others might feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean your mom or Naoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, both.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your beef bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you go around town making deliveries, have you heard anything about Naoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Detective Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,got in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With who?{don't change it to "whom," casualshit etc}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was arguing with an officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, he frequently criticized how they were handling the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto's obsession with the case seemed abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why he was so fixated on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way the police treated him like a kid might've had something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika knew all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she only told us that he was fighting with an officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know? That lame cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So he's super stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's surprisingly emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a picture of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it remind you of those secret hideouts in live-action shows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard those are really tough shoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all dusty and hot as Hell with the bright lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't the buildings and events in this world made from people's repressed emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what Naoto said on the Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the chosen day forth, I shall walk a completely different path in life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Naoto was rejecting his life as a boy detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This secret lab...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like one of those old sets where boy detectives or heroes solve cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if this came from Naoto's mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he isn't as grown up as he looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about any of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I do know one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,running away from something too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warning! Intruders!{lol iphone alarm}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Looks like you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dealing with this child has been quite a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No, no, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Naoto's Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, heads up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're bear-low us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless speaking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you leaving me here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I always left all alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wear the same face as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if you're implying we're one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the difference between you and me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why delude yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the truth, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These childish gestures are no mere affectation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto, don't argue with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has to face this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't we...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all had to go through this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fools all say it, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're only a child! Just a measly kid!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they need it, you're an ace detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once you're done,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's back to the playpen with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't the means to deal with society's two-faced nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a lonely child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be a big boy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they'll see who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a reason for me to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can find my own reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are but a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you change that essential truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At your core,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you admire the sort of "strong" and "cool" men who populate detective fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in trying to emulate them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must know that, in truth, you're nothing of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirogane Naoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a cool, masculine name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a name doesn't change the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't let you cross...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the barrier between sexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you become an ideal man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you were never male to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I hear that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's not a guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't throw a tantrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That accomplishes nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How often I've heard those words from the adults!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Throwing a tantrum won't solve anything, Naoto."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They made you cry, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet here you are, mimicking those same men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are you trying to justify?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't suffer anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know exactly how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I am you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let her get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:20:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll continue to suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Shadow... The true self...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just gotta do our thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and kick the Shadow's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you act so almighty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}hate{\i0} violent guys who let their emotions get the best of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's body-altering time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sick of yourselves too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:22:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin the special operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she modify my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this isn't a modification.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't modify you in that sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She made you older!{lolwut}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yo-Yo-Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Those wrinkles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liver spots!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.51,0:22:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:07.10,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I look at the rustic scenery
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:09.82,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}along the path to school
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:15.57,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}we walked together {kimi to aruita tsuugakuro hinabiru keshiki mitsumete}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.08,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Campus in spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:24.46,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}the summer festival {haru no koutei kasenshiki natsu matsuri}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:28.71,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}These were the days we spent
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:31.71,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}shoulder-to-shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:36.51,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}laughing together {minna de waratte katayose sugoshiteta hibi}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:44.07,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}From past to present {kono ninake nai nichijou wo nagamete}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.85,0:23:48.23,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I've always
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.23,0:23:50.65,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}looked back on these
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:53.69,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}carefree days {kako kara ima made sugoshite kita yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:24:01.58,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}From today to tomorrow {kyou kara asu ashita kara mirai he}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:14.05,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\t(\b0\c&H303030&\3c&HFFFFFF&)}We move forward while treasuring the bonds we've made {minna to kizuita kizuna himete aruki dasu}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me alter your bodies already!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.66,0:24:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.39,0:24:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been so good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.25,0:24:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's one crazy lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.09,0:24:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one needs me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.97,0:24:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.03,0:24:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so full of life!
